Bruce Yarnell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bruce_Yarnell 0 Bruce Yarnell (December 28, 1935 – November 30, 1973) was an American actor who co-starred in the second, final season (1961–1962) of NBC's two-season Western television series Outlaws, set in the lawless Oklahoma Territory. He was also a noted Broadway and opera baritone.
